Articles.Content: Hi everyone. I\'m new to the forum, but not KSP. I\'ve been playing for a while, and I\'m running out of things to do after i finally succeeded in my orbital rendzvous and mun landing. Any ideas what to do next?

Welcome to the KSP Forums!

Look around the forums, there are a number of posts tagged with [Challenge] in the title where people have set some criteria for a mission like challenge.

Happy Launching!

Arrr!

Capt\'n Skunky

KSP Community Manager

GREETINGS! FROM BEYOND THE VEIL OF THE INTERNETS!

If you\'re looking for something to do, try landing on the Mun without any Solid Rocket Boosters(SRBs), or even the other way around,

try getting there without any Liquid engines!

There are plenty O\' parts to download here on the forums, so variety is abound!

Happy launchings!
